me. Ebina has taken over Mamoru Takabe&#39;s role in the Seiryu Clan in his absence.</p><p> Kazuma Kiryu, the playable protagonist of the majority of the previous entries, appears in <em>Like A Dragon: Infinite Wealth</em> for “one final battle”. In the game, Kiryu has been diagnosed with cancer, though it&#39;s not known what his prognosis is.</p><p> <em>Like A Dragon: Infinite Wealth</em> comes to <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps4">PS4</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> on January 26, 2024. </p><figure id="attachment_3501097" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3501097" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3501097" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/danny-trejo-like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3501097" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth&#39; Credit: Sega</figcaption></figure><p> There are three different editions of the game. The Standard edition includes the game and is priced at $69.99. However, the Deluxe edition contains the game and the Master Vacation Bundle for $84.99.</p><p> Those able to splash the cash can shell out for the Ultimate edition which has the game, the Master Vacation Bundle, Assorted Outfit Bundle, Sujimon &amp; Resort Bundle and the <em>Yakuza</em> CD Collection Set.</p><p> All pre-orders will benefit from the Hero&#39;s Booster Pack, which increases party members&#39; level and job rank by one, and the Special Job set. These are Linebacker and Tennis Ace, though they are restricted to only male party members for the Linebacker and only female party members for the Tennis Ace.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a> said it was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/larian-studios-reacts-to-baldurs-gate-3-being-underestimated-3501048">understandable</a> that some might have misjudged <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em></a> &#39;s potential success.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-reveals-danny-trejo-as-a-hawaiian-mob-boss-3501078">&#39;Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth&#39; reveals Danny Trejo as a Hawaiian mob boss</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
